Package: twitterfeatures
Type: Package
Title: Simple Feature Engineering Functions for Twitter Data
Version: 0.1.0
Depends: R (>= 3.4.0)
Authors@R: c(person("Sebastian", "Fox", , "sebastian.fox@phe.gov.uk", c("aut", "cre")))
Maintainer: Sebastian Fox <sebastian.fox@phe.gov.uk>
Description: When attempting machine learning on Twitter data a typical task is to 
    create features that can be used to train and test models on. This package 
    standardises methods of creating those features.
